#: kb/models.py:1176
msgid ""
"How long an administrator may stay inactive inside Django Admin after "
"completing the extra admin MFA check. Default is 600 seconds (10 minutes). "
"Minimum enforced by code is 60 seconds; maximum enforced by code is 86400 "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh pentadbir boleh kekal tidak aktif dalam Django Admin selepas "
"melengkapkan semakan MFA pentadbir tambahan. Lalai ialah 600 saat (10 "
"minit). Minimum yang dikuatkuasakan oleh kod ialah 60 saat; maksimum ialah "
"86400 saat."

#: kb/admin.py:253 kb/models.py:1101
msgid ""
"How long deleted published articles remain recoverable in My Profile → Admin"
" tools → Deletion queue before permanent deletion. Default is 7 days. Set to"
" 0 to permanently delete published articles immediately after MFA "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh artikel diterbitkan yang dipadam kekal boleh dipulihkan dalam Profil "
"Saya → Alat pentadbir → Baris gilir pemadaman sebelum pemadaman kekal. Lalai"
" ialah 7 hari. Tetapkan kepada 0 untuk memadam artikel diterbitkan secara "
"kekal serta-merta selepas pengesahan MFA."

#: kb/admin.py:260
msgid ""
"How long failed-login/MFA escalation history is remembered without a "
"successful login. Successful verification clears it immediately. Default is "
"604800 seconds (7 days)."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh sejarah peningkatan log masuk/MFA yang gagal diingati tanpa log masuk"
" berjaya. Pengesahan yang berjaya mengosongkannya serta-merta. Lalai ialah "
"604800 saat (7 hari)."

#: kb/models.py:1167
msgid ""
"How long failed-login/MFA lockout history is remembered if the user never "
"signs in successfully. Successful password/MFA verification resets the "
"relevant lockout history immediately. Default is 604800 seconds (7 days)."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh sejarah sekatan log masuk/MFA yang gagal diingati jika pengguna tidak"
" pernah berjaya log masuk. Pengesahan kata laluan/MFA yang berjaya "
"menetapkan semula sejarah sekatan yang berkaitan serta-merta. Lalai ialah "
"604800 saat (7 hari)."

#: kb/admin.py:263 kb/models.py:1228
msgid "How long the login/MFA check is blocked after this stage triggers."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh semakan log masuk/MFA disekat selepas peringkat ini dicetuskan."

#: kb/admin.py:264 kb/models.py:1233
msgid ""
"How many lockouts should use this stage before moving to the next stage. Use"
